- [ ] Community heat is high
- [ ] Niche durability is strong
- [ ] Social moat potential exists

### Gate 3: Validation Plan
- [ ] Validation plan includes 8-12 tests
- [ ] All required test types included
- [ ] Test thresholds are specific and actionable
- [ ] Kill/pivot/proceed rules are clear
