## Mental Model

**Heat gets you in. Durability makes it a real SaaS business.**

This playbook validates both:
- **Heat Filter (Isenberg)**: "Do a tribe of real humans urgently want this?" (Steps 1-8)
- **Durability Filter**: "Will this still matter and keep paying 12–36 months from now?" (Steps 9-11)

Only ideas that pass both filters proceed to engineering.
